        "content": "import torch\n\n\n@torch.no_grad()\ndef run(\n    attn_output: torch.Tensor,\n    residual: torch.Tensor,\n    o_proj_weight: torch.Tensor,\n) -> torch.Tensor:\n    \"\"\"\n    Fused attention output projection with residual addition.\n\n    # beta=0 matmul keeps cuBLAS's normal heuristic algo (addmm beta=1.0\n    # regressed every shape in this problem \u2014 likely disables split-K).\n    \"\"\"\n    projected = torch.matmul(attn_output, o_proj_weight.t())\n    projected.add_(residual)\n    return projected\n"
